&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been diving into binary exploitation for the past three months, and honestly, it&amp;rsquo;s been a wild journey! ☠️ If you don’t know, binary exploitation is all about finding bugs in programs and using them to break stuff (in a good way, of course). I got into it because I’m super into cybersecurity and hacking, and this stuff is just next level. In this post, I’ll walk you through a pwn challenge I could solve.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
